    "content": "Tired Of Toein\u2019 The Line\r\nThis the only single by Rocky Burnette (son of Fifties legend Johnny \r\nBurnette). Released in 79/80 it was a worldwide hit everywhere but here in \r\nThe UK - #58. Tab by bass50611. Very catchy tune. Not exact but this what \r\nI Would play on stage. Symbols \u2018.\u2019 Are pauses dots\r\nComments at bass254@btinternet.com \r\n \r\n[tab]Intro:                                 (Play This Bit x2)\r\nG|----3------------------------3-------------------|\r\nD|-5-----2--5-----3---------5-----2--5-----3-------|\r\nA|-------------3-----5------------------3-----5----|\r\nE|----------------------3------------------------3-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 1:                               (Play This Bit x4)\r\nG|----3------------------------3-------------------|\r\nD|-5-----2--5-----3---------5-----2--5-----3-------|\r\nA|-------------3-----5------------------3-----5----|\r\nE|----------------------3------------------------3-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Bridge:\r\nG|------------------------------------4--4-4--4--------------4--4-4--4-|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-3--3-3--3---2--2-2--2---3--3-3--3-------------3--3-3--3-------------|\r\nE|---------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------|\r\nD|-5--------------5--7----|\r\nA|----7--5--7--8--------7-|\r\nE|------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 2:                               (Play This Bit x4)\r\nG|----3------------------------3-------------------|\r\nD|-5-----2--5-----3---------5-----2--5-----3-------|\r\nA|-------------3-----5------------------3-----5----|\r\nE|----------------------3------------------------3-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Bridge:\r\nG|------------------------------------4--4-4--4--------------4--4-4--4-|\r\nD|---------------------------------------------------------------------|\r\nA|-3--3-3--3---2--2-2--2---3--3-3--3-------------3--3-3--3-------------|\r\nE|---------------------------------------------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------|\r\nD|-5--------------5--7----|\r\nA|----7--5--7--8--------7-|\r\nE|------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 3:                               (Play This Bit x2)\r\nG|----3------------------------3-------------------|\r\nD|-5-----2--5-----3---------5-----2--5-----3-------|\r\nA|-------------3-----5------------------3-----5----|\r\nE|----------------------3------------------------3-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Interlude:       \u2018.\u2019                 \u2018.\u2019\r\nG|-5----5--------------5----5-------------5----5---|\r\nD|---5----5---5----------5----5---5---------5----5-|\r\nA|-------------7-5-----------------7-5-------------|\r\nE|----------------7-------------------7------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[tab]                        (Break)\r\nG|--------------------------|\r\nD|-5------------------------|\r\nA|--7-5----4--5--5--5--5--5-|\r\nE|------7-------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Verse 4:                               (Play This Bit x2)\r\nG|----3------------------------3-------------------|\r\nD|-5-----2--5-----3---------5-----2--5-----3-------|\r\nA|-------------3-----5------------------3-----5----|\r\nE|----------------------3------------------------3-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]Outro:                               (Repeat To Fade/End)\r\nG|----3----------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-5-----2--5-----3---------5--5---2--2--------------|\r\nA|-------------3-----5-------------------3--3---5--5-|\r\nE|----------------------3----------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nSymbols \u2018.\u2019 Are Pause Dots\r\n\r\nMay Grateful Thanks To KRAZIEKHAT For The Chords",
